title: Tiny Salmon!
author: Hopsoplo
pages:
#- Tiny salmon!
Tiny salmon! Swimming
up a river chasing
that impossible
dreeeeeeeeeam!
The mother bird say,
"Caw caw caw!"
The Chimpanzee say,
"eaaaaaaaeaeeaaah!"
The friendly owl say,
"Hoo! Hoo hoo hoo!"
But the salmon can only say,
